110. J Feline Med Surg. 2021 Mar;23(3):211-233. doi: 10.1177/1098612X21993657.

2021 AAHA/AAFP Feline Life Stage Guidelines.

Quimby J(1), Gowland S(2), Carney HC(3), DePorter T(4), Plummer P(5), Westropp 
J(6).

Author information:
(1)DVM, PhD, DACVIM, Co-Chair of 2021 AAHA/AAFP Feline Life Stage Guidelines 
Task Force The Ohio State University, Department of Veterinary Clinical 
Sciences, Columbus, Ohio, USA.
(2)DVM, DABVP, Co-Chair of 2021 AAHA/AAFP Feline Life Stage Guidelines Task 
Force OVC Smith Lane Animal Hospital, Ontario Veterinary College, Guelph, 
Ontario, Canada.
(3)DVM, MS, DABVP, WestVet Emergency and Specialty Center, Garden City, Idaho, 
USA.
(4)DVM, MRCVS, DACVB, DECAWBM, Oakland Veterinary Referral Services, Bloomfield 
Hills, Michigan, USA.
(5)LVT, VTS (ECC, SAIM), Texas A&M University Veterinary Medical Teaching 
Hospital, College Station, Texas, USA.
