Expanding the Coverage of Metabolic Landscape in Cultivated Rice with Integrated 
Computational Approaches.

Li X(1), Zhou H(1), Xiao N(2), Wu X(3), Shan Y(3), Chen L(1), Wang C(3), Wang 
Z(3), Huang J(4), Li A(5), Li X(6).

Author information:
(1)CAS Key Laboratory of Synthetic Biology / National Center for Gene Research, 
CAS Center for Excellence in Molecular Plant Sciences / Institute of Plant 
Physiology and Ecology, Chinese Academy of Sciences, Shanghai 200032, China; 
University of Chinese Academy of Sciences, Beijing 100049, China.
(2)Lixiahe Agricultural Research Institute of Jiangsu Province, Yangzhou 225007, 
China.
(3)CAS Key Laboratory of Synthetic Biology / National Center for Gene Research, 
CAS Center for Excellence in Molecular Plant Sciences / Institute of Plant 
Physiology and Ecology, Chinese Academy of Sciences, Shanghai 200032, China.
(4)Shanghai Key Laboratory of Plant Molecular Sciences, College of Life 
Sciences, Shanghai Normal University, Shanghai 200234, China. Electronic 
