Spatiotemporal trends in stroke burden and mortality attributable to household 
air pollution from solid fuels in 204 countries and territories from 1990 to 
2019.

Lu H(1), Tan Z(2), Liu Z(2), Wang L(3), Wang Y(1), Suo C(4), Zhang T(4), Jin 
L(2), Dong Q(1), Cui M(5), Jiang Y(6), Chen X(7).

